Admiralty Circle plaza dị na Eti-Osa Local Government Area nke Lagos State na Nigeria
E guzobere ya iji nakọta ụgwọ n'okporo ụzọ 49 kilomita na LekkiʹEti-Osa Expressway
Ọ bụ nkwekọrịta Public Private Partnership (PPP) n'etiti gọọmentị Lagos State na Messrs ikeja Concession Company Limited LCC. Ọrụ malitere n'ọma ahịa ahụ n'ụbọchị nke 5 nke ọnwa Jenụwarị , 2011.
